    <h1 class="H1-Signup">Create your very own <br /> personal bookshelf</h1>
    <h5 class="H5-Signup">Join for free to save your favorite books!</h5>
    <a href="/auth/signup"><button class="Signup-button">Sign up</button></a>
  </div>
</div>